Once you want to build your game for a release, you should disable the automatic file creation and editing. To do this, add the following line to the plugin creation: YarnSlingerPlugin::new()
// ...
.with_development_file_generation(DevelopmentFileGeneration::None) This will change the behavior of missing translations to simply fall back to the base localization. While you're on it, you might also want to disable Bevy's hot reloading.

